@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.20 - v1 + 0.26)) - ((v1 + 0.72 - v0 + 0.03) + v2))
    v2 = wp.cos(0.92)
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.29) - ((v1 + 0.00 / v1 + 0.56) + (v1 + 0.74 * v1 + 0.44)))
    tmp = wp.sin(v2)
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.10 / tmp + 0.89)) * 0.38)
    data[tid] = v0
